  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>Distress screening group</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Physical activities will be monitored by wearable device. Patient-reported outcomes including distress, depression, physical activities and quality of life are going to be collected by questionnaires based on smartphone application and paper. The algorithm of distress screening will be developed with the analysis of patterns of physical activities.</description>
  </arm_group>
